{
  "3259600": {
    "name": "红色的炼金术士和白色的守护者 ～蕾斯莱莉娅娜的炼金工房～",
    "steam_appid": 3259600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>两人为寻回重要的东西，在失落的故乡寻找真相——</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜＜原野＞＞</h2>在能展现昼夜变化与天气变化等多彩景致的原野中，尽情享受战斗与采集吧！<br>莉雅丝与史雷的操作可随时切换，两人各自能够进行的原野动作也有所不同。<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/ec56ad733c422dc39e8d6a494577f2b3.poster.avif?t=1760598454\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/ec56ad733c422dc39e8d6a494577f2b3.webm?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/ec56ad733c422dc39e8d6a494577f2b3.mp4?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜＜亚界之道＞＞</h2>在每次挑战时地图与出现的魔物都会变化的层层迷宫“亚界之道”中，难度越高，就能获得越珍贵的素材。<br>从强敌或宝箱中，还有机会获得稀有装备品“星珠”。<br>以更高品质的调合素材与“星珠”为目标，挑战“亚界之道”吧！<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/0f14ccf3ed66e60fc395f56854d1206f.poster.avif?t=1760598454\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/0f14ccf3ed66e60fc395f56854d1206f.webm?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/0f14ccf3ed66e60fc395f56854d1206f.mp4?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜＜战斗＞＞</h2>本作战斗系统是富有战略性的时间条指令战斗。<br>战斗成员分为前卫与后卫两组，每组最多三人。在体验与伙伴齐心协力作战的乐趣之余，还可运用多重行动、道具调合或联手攻击等，展开更加畅快淋漓的战斗对抗！<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/4bb2a6b503aa6969af1f68837f643d49.poster.avif?t=1760598454\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/4bb2a6b503aa6969af1f68837f643d49.webm?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/4bb2a6b503aa6969af1f68837f643d49.mp4?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/01858964d57fce4b18c10868967723d8.poster.avif?t=1760598454\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/01858964d57fce4b18c10868967723d8.webm?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/01858964d57fce4b18c10868967723d8.mp4?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/1da08c3716bbe169efc4bb370a5adf1f.poster.avif?t=1760598454\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/1da08c3716bbe169efc4bb370a5adf1f.webm?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/1da08c3716bbe169efc4bb370a5adf1f.mp4?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜＜调合＞＞</h2>以简单却深奥的“天赋颜色调合”系统创造出属于自己的道具吧！<br>只要将素材的“天赋颜色”连接后投入，该素材的特性就能继承到成品之中。<br>再加入特定素材时，甚至还能解锁全新的配方。<br>在最多 3 个调整栏位中投入素材，还能进一步强化成品的性能！<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/f07de24c57b455d86f4a6c89966e050e.poster.avif?t=1760598454\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/f07de24c57b455d86f4a6c89966e050e.webm?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/f07de24c57b455d86f4a6c89966e050e.mp4?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/1e3e53609b61bffa9225096f39d57077.poster.avif?t=1760598454\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/1e3e53609b61bffa9225096f39d57077.webm?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/1e3e53609b61bffa9225096f39d57077.mp4?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜＜城镇发展 / 商店经营＞＞</h2>在自己的商店内贩卖“调合”制成的道具，推动城镇的发展吧！<br>通过贩卖各种各样的道具赚取资金，再将受益投入城镇建设来推动发展。<br>随着城镇日益繁盛，可获得新的调合配方，或推进主线剧情。<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/05c48ba6d12622673aafac090f88d79f.poster.avif?t=1760598454\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/05c48ba6d12622673aafac090f88d79f.webm?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/05c48ba6d12622673aafac090f88d79f.mp4?t=1760598454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜＜角色＞＞</h2>莉雅丝·艾德莱森（CV：立花 日菜）<br>史雷·库洛斯利塔（CV：土岐 隼一）<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/10335a46ce4a9f50110f1c26a033159f.avif?t=1760598454\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras_big/10335a46ce4a9f50110f1c26a033159f.avif?t=1760598454 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/90637b0547e2037dc1188a40063100c6.avif?t=1760598454\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras_big/90637b0547e2037dc1188a40063100c6.avif?t=1760598454 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>·历代“炼金工房”系列的部分角色也将作为可操作角色登场！<br>罗杰路克斯·麦臣<br>托托莉亚·赫尔默德<br>薇尔贝儿·沃·耶斯礼特<br>苏菲·诺伊恩缪拉<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/93ab9e147196a2af4e59e612dda64d90.avif?t=1760598454\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>·此外，还有历代“炼金工房”系列角色将会大量登场<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259600/extras/85aa0631c9a73c7b4fb8ea42cc55aff9.avif?t=1760598454\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >＜＜故事＞＞</h2>曾经，在三州交界处，坐落着一座因矿山与贸易而繁荣的城镇——赫尔芬。<br>然而一场神秘的灾害，却让生活在这座安宁小镇的绝大多数居民，消失得无影无踪。<br>此后城镇被列为禁区，除王都派遣的调查员之外，任何人都不得进入。<br><br>岁月流转，城镇被解除封锁，复兴计划也提上日程。<br>曾经被迫离乡的少年与少女，也怀着各自的目的重返家乡。<br>少女的心愿是重建行踪不明的祖父留下的店铺，少年则是为了调查父亲留下的遗物。<br>两人因共同的目标——查明当年居民消失的真相——<br><br>而在故土相遇，携手踏上探寻真相的旅程。<br>殊不知在前方等待着他们的，是超乎想象的邂逅与真相。<br><br>※详情请参阅官方网站。<br>※包含本商品的其他版本也正在贩售。请留意避免重复购买。",
